    "name": "[Agoda Pick] Mini Hotel May Nampo",
    "detail": "I spent 4 nights at this hotel and had a fabulous stay. The room was comfortable and pleasant. I selected a standard Y room and there were huge windows on two sides with fantastic views of Busan Tower, Biff Square the harbor and the mountains. The hotel is located right in the middle of Nampodong, with the subway station and the shopping district right out of the door. Moreover, the Lotte Dept Store, Gukje Market, Jagalchi Market, Yongdusan and Biff Sq are all within a 5min walk. Depiste being in such a busy district, the room was really quiet. I'll be booking again the next time I visit Busan!",
